---
import { AlertDisplayCards } from './AlertCards';
---

<section id="ai" class="relative py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Animated alert cards with AI triage -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <AlertDisplayCards client:visible />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Copy -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <span class="text-heading bg-heading/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-medium text-xs">AI Triage</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-heading mt-4 mb-4">
          Your model. Your data.<br/>Your confidence thresholds.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text leading-relaxed mb-6">
          AI triage is a playbook action &mdash; not a black box. Call it from any playbook, set your own thresholds, and keep humans in the loop for anything below your confidence bar. No data leaves your network if you don't want it to.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-text">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-heading">Bring your own LLM</strong> &mdash; Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, or fully local with Ollama</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-heading">Structured assessments</strong> &mdash; severity, determination, confidence score, reasoning chain</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-heading">You control the thresholds</strong> &mdash; auto-resolve at 90% confidence, escalate at 70%, queue the rest</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-success mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span><strong class="text-heading">Full audit trail</strong> &mdash; every AI decision logged with inputs, outputs, and reasoning</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
